cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.NA 

The paper deals with the reconstruction of cardiac MRI images using deep learning and regularization techniques. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The use of prior information and regularization techniques also suggests the involvement of information theory (cs.IT) and numerical analysis (cs.NA). Additionally, the use of highly undersampled measurements and the need for efficient computation suggests the involvement of multimedia (cs.MM) as well.
